01:40:56,718 --> 01:40:58,345
Well, I was hoping
your mom and dad

1258
01:40:58,428 --> 01:40:59,638
would make me feel better,

1259
01:40:59,721 --> 01:41:02,390
but it doesn't seem to be
turning out so good.

1260
01:41:03,099 --> 01:41:05,185
Would you like to go
to a hospital?

1261
01:41:05,977 --> 01:41:08,063
Hospital won't fix me.

1262
01:41:13,652 --> 01:41:15,111
But maybe you could, though.

1263
01:41:15,195 --> 01:41:16,488
You could help.

1264
01:41:17,364 --> 01:41:18,365
How?

1265
01:41:19,241 --> 01:41:20,408
Well, at school,

1266
01:41:21,576 --> 01:41:25,080
bring an object from each
of your classmates home to me.

1267
01:41:26,164 --> 01:41:27,332
That might work.

1268
01:41:28,708 --> 01:41:30,293
How will that make you better?

1269
01:41:34,005 --> 01:41:36,132
It might be just what I need.

1270
01:41:39,302 --> 01:41:41,805
And if you got better,
you'd go back home?

1271
01:41:45,767 --> 01:41:47,269
If I got better...

1272
01:41:49,604 --> 01:41:51,022
I'd go back home.

1273
01:42:52,000 --> 01:42:53,001
Alex.

1274
01:42:54,961 --> 01:42:56,504
What are you doing in here?

1275
01:42:56,588 --> 01:42:59,132
Um, I didn't
feel like playing,

1276
01:42:59,215 --> 01:43:01,217
and I forgot something.

1277
01:43:02,635 --> 01:43:04,596
Whoa, whoa, whoa.
Hey, hey, hey.

1278
01:43:08,058 --> 01:43:09,059
Are you okay?

1279
01:43:09,684 --> 01:43:11,144
- Yeah.
- Yeah?

1280
01:43:12,103 --> 01:43:14,773
You've been
awful quiet lately.

1281
01:43:15,440 --> 01:43:16,608
Quieter than usual.

1282
01:43:17,275 --> 01:43:18,318
How are you doing?

1283
01:43:18,860 --> 01:43:21,321
I'm okay.
I just forgot something.

1284
01:43:22,238 --> 01:43:23,239
It's okay.

1285
01:43:25,367 --> 01:43:26,826
Alex, you know,

1286
01:43:26,910 --> 01:43:29,537
if... you ever want to talk
to someone,

1287
01:43:30,038 --> 01:43:31,456
you can always talk to me.

1288
01:43:33,041 --> 01:43:34,250
Do you know that?

1289
01:43:34,334 --> 01:43:35,418
Yeah.

1290
01:43:35,502 --> 01:43:37,754
You can talk to me
about anything you want.

1291
01:43:41,257 --> 01:43:42,634
I wanna go back now.

1292
01:43:44,552 --> 01:43:46,513
Okay. Go play.

1293
01:44:43,820 --> 01:44:45,071
