1294
01:46:33,221 --> 01:46:34,222
No...

1295
01:46:44,023 --> 01:46:46,276
<i>Stephen here suffered
a stroke a little while back,</i>

1296
01:46:46,359 --> 01:46:48,152
<i>so he's unable to speak.</i>

1297
01:46:48,236 --> 01:46:50,822
<i>And I'm taking care of
the family for the time being.</i>

1298
01:46:51,322 --> 01:46:53,032
I'm glad you both are here.

1299
01:46:53,116 --> 01:46:55,243
Alex, how are you doing, pal?

1300
01:46:55,326 --> 01:46:56,578
I'm okay.

1301
01:46:56,661 --> 01:46:58,204
Now, we're gonna
ask you some questions

1302
01:46:58,288 --> 01:47:00,123
about what happened
at school, okay?

1303
01:47:02,458 --> 01:47:04,294
Tomorrow,
people will come here.

1304
01:47:05,920 --> 01:47:07,839
And they will search
this house...

1305
01:47:12,510 --> 01:47:14,304
and we have to be ready.

1306
01:47:33,740 --> 01:47:35,199
Detective, come in!

1307
01:47:35,283 --> 01:47:36,284
Good morning, Ms. Lilly.

1308
01:47:36,367 --> 01:47:37,535
- How are you today?
- Fine.

1309
01:47:37,619 --> 01:47:39,370
- Good to see you again.
- Nice to see you too.

1310
01:47:39,454 --> 01:47:41,080
