- Oh, yes.

1311
01:47:41,164 --> 01:47:43,541
We just wanted to come by the
house for a few minutes today

1312
01:47:43,625 --> 01:47:44,834
and look around, uh,

1313
01:47:44,917 --> 01:47:47,795
see the environment
that Alex has been living in.

1314
01:47:47,879 --> 01:47:51,341
And just get an idea of what
the family dynamic is like.

1315
01:47:51,424 --> 01:47:53,593
