Jeremy,
there's glass everywhere.

1366
02:00:22,049 --> 02:00:23,801
Find her shoe! My god!

1367
02:00:23,884 --> 02:00:25,302
Oh, my God. Oh, my God.

1368
02:00:25,386 --> 02:00:27,096
Now there's a man
in the kitchen!

